item.title: Help with errors(im a noob so i need good details)
item.dc:creator: @Aero_Mist Aero Mist
item.description:
@Aero_Mist wrote:

open up client.java then click alt + f. You should get a search pop-up. Put public void globalobjects() into the search line. Click find next. Make sure your at the top of the file, if your not scroll up. From there you should the makeGlobalObject(, 6951, -1, 10);//floorghjkiyu. You then have two choices. Either delete it, or edit it. Since i dont know where it should be i suggest you delete all 3 of them. Dont delete anything extra though. Should work then :D. If your intrested in adding objects i suggest checking out this guide.
